Register for an account
http://www.npaci.edu/DICE/SRB/install/SRBUserRegister.html
Project Name: SCEC ITR
Project PI: Tom Jordan

Three ways to access from UNIX
1) Scommand - commmand line utilities
2) MySRB - web bases GUI interface
3) API libraries - access from within C, Java & Python programs

SCOMMANDS INSTALLATION

Download the latest source code from:
http://www.npaci.edu/DICE/SRB/tarfiles/main.html
Contact Sheau-Yen Chen <sheauc@sdsc.edu> for the PGP key and unlock the tar file.

$  ./configure
$  gmake

add utilities/bin/ to your $PATH and utilities/man/man1/ to your $MANPATH

$  mkdir $HOME/.srb

Make a file $HOME/.srb/.MdasEnv containg:
  mdasCollectionHome '/home/<yoursrbusername>.<yoursrbdomainname>'
  mdasDomainHome '<yoursrbdomainname>'
  srbUser '<yoursrbusername>'
  srbHost 'srb.sdsc.edu'
  srbPort '6850'
  defaultResource 'sfs-scec'

Make a file $HOME/.srb/.MdasAuth containg:
  <yoursrbpassword>

$  Shelp       # for a list of Scommands.
